snippet.title: Liminal Phase - Official Pico 4 Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: This very short teaser trailer for Liminal Phase reveals that the VR action horror game is coming to Pico 4 on December 21, 2023. Liminal Phase is also available on Meta Quest App Lab, Steam VR, Viveport, and Vive XR Elite. Liminal Phase is set in a parallel ‘90s. Fight malevolent monsters, solve peculiar puzzles, and explore the dark corners of a fractured mind consumed by video games.
